    OUT_SOURCE_PATH SOURCE_PATH
    REPO eliaskosunen/scnlib
    REF v0.3
    SHA512 91ab0ff5d7d2e4a4924bfa00cafc49c3b0d88b87f4adbdce786be0f51913e3c61c6948c27da6af1e020646e610540dc63323fbf7b59f9210266f1ba79bf95adc
